## How This Applies to Your System

### Character Voice (characters.md)
- Each character has a distinctive voice (like a singer)
- Readers recognize them by how they think/speak
- Voice filters observations through character's unique lens

### Hook Section (7-point structure)
- Your opening should establish voice
- Should invite the reader: "Come in here"
- Should work as a doorway for YOU (the writer) too
- Take time with it (King spends months/years)

### Per-Chapter Review (write-review-cycle.md)
- **Consistency check** ensures voice stays distinctive
- **Read aloud** catches when voice shifts
- **Early detection** prevents voice drift across chapters
- Your review catches what King has to wait until the end to fix

### AI Slop Detection (ai-slop-detection.md)
- Removes anything that muddies your voice
- Deletes vague attribution ("essentially," "basically")
- Flags inflated language (opposite of clean voice)
- Flags rhetorical questions (false vulnerability, not your authentic voice)
- **Goal:** Keep it sounding like YOU, not a writing tool

